<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hl jlst fy hdwʾ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hl jlst fy hdwʾ ṭrt llʿlạʾ
 wtạ̉mlt ṣlybạaⁿ byn ạ̉rḍ wsmạʾ

[V2]
 fwqh ạlḥb tjly̱ bjrạḥ wdmạʾ
 ṣạfḥạ ʿn ṣạlbyh bṣlạj wdʿạʾ(2)

[V3]
 ạlqrạr- yzyḥ ạljbạl ynạdy tʿạl bṣwt yhz ạlḍmyr

[V4]
 ysẖyʿ ạlslạm ynyr ạlẓlạm fybṣr ḥty̱ ạlḍryr

[V5]
 2- msḥ ạldmʿ ạlskyb mn ʿywn ạlbsṭạʾ
 nạzʿạ ḥzn ạlḥzạny̱ zạrʿạ fyhm ʿzạʾ

[V6]
 gẖạfrạ kl ạlkẖṭạyạ sẖạfyạ mn fyh dạʾ
 rạfʿạ kl ạlblạyạ dạfʿạ kl ạlsẖqạʾ(2)

[V7]
 3- hl tdẖwqt slạmạ wnʿmt bạlfdạʾ
 mn msyḥ bdmạh ạ̹jzl lk ạlʿṭạʾ

[V8]
 rạḍyạ ḍḥy̱ gẖnạh ḥty̱ ygẖny ạlfqrạʾ
 jạʾ llạ̹nsạn nwrạ mạnḥạ lh ạlḍyạʾ(2)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>10439</hymn_number>
</song>